      <a href="https://github.com/jordannewell" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-green">github</a>
      <span class="mx-2">·</span>
      <a href="mailto:hello@jordannewell.com" class="hover:text-green">hello</a>
    </p>
    <p class="mb-2">
